Package: echoflow
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, fcitx5, pipewire-bin
Description: Offline voice input method for Fcitx5
 EchoFlow is an offline voice input method for deepin and Fcitx5.
 It ships a native daemon, Fcitx5 addon, Qt/DTK settings UI, and
 qwen-asr runtime integration. Model weights are downloaded from the
 settings UI after installation and are not included in this package.
